{"tid":1759644,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"咩浪漫主義，送頭，戀戰，真係好難聽...大家唔好再咁講","createTime":"2019-11-27T19:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T07:22:45.000Z","uid":2746,"like":9,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f238301ca6e44e6cd102a5ef7cee265cacb9be60","tid":1759644,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T19:14:32.000Z","msg":"記唔記得我哋7月1號絕望嘅氣氛下<br />\n前線明知送頭，明知冇得翻出嚟<br />\n用必死嘅心態去佔領立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先開啟左抗爭嘅道路<br />\n就結果論當然無人批評<br />\n<br />\n到理工大學俾狗圍攻<br />\n就一大堆冷氣軍師出嚟話<br />\n打陣地戰係送頭 ,黑警係圍點打援反包無用 <br />\n仲衝去poly係浪漫主義<br />\n幾十人逃出poly ,幾百人外面被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話值唔值得 ,要計數當然係唔值得<br />\n但係大家就係有依份勇氣<br />\n願意為咗未知結果付出<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前線有時係有少少唔理性<br />\n但如果大家都好似冷氣軍師咁理性<br />\n運動都唔會行得到去今時今日</span><br />\n所以希望大家<br />\n唔好再用依一類字眼批評前線嘅手足<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ba1cfc0ea5c13c1a04177a77454b1df94a0646","tid":1759644,"uid":200666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T19:18:27.000Z","msg":"難聽過粗口"},{"pid":"7fcb228e70ef22e51808aaadcdc6357e84a46668","tid":1759644,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T19:25:46.000Z","msg":"大家唔好再咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27521511734a79aec23482d79444289a178f6d1f","tid":1759644,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T19:25:58.000Z","msg":"大家唔好再咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 